  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tribe members are waiting for your help!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to the last drop of your blood, choose the best options, and save the tribe members. Stand against waves of creatures, collect as many moon stones as you can, and enhance your weapons to survive longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156110/extras/1dc218a5554da2679513fdc9b00851c0.poster.avif?t=1737517014\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156110/extras/1dc218a5554da2679513fdc9b00851c0.webm?t=1737517014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156110/extras/1dc218a5554da2679513fdc9b00851c0.mp4?t=1737517014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of weapons and spells, each with different abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters with different weapons and powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A customizable gameplay experience with choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waves of incoming creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade characters with the gold you earn</p></li></ul>",
